// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0370 — Mass File Rename (worldleaks)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 7b99594a-b127-5746-833e-19bd44e9425a

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
